bearmail (0.3.4) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fixed bugs in bearmail_sieve scripts & make them compatibles with roundcube
  * Remove bashism in bearmail.postinst
  * Gave up with the 'bearmail-' prefix for config files, again.
  * review bearmail-switch
  * configure bearmail-switch for bearmail-antivirus
  * review bearmail-switch script
  * Force mailmap var in bearmail-update
  * bearmail-antispam and bearmail-web removed
  * bearmail-antivirus now use clamav-milter

 -- Benjamin LINET <blinet@bearstech.com>  Sat, 19 Nov 2011 23:00:58 +0200

